{
  "stem": "18056.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 589.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some cemeteries around there and they would bury them there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, quite a few.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I say, being that we had a-- quite a large family supposedly, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you had no way to go from here to the other side-- end of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't even know whether he is alive or dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was not-- it was not a way to-- to really analyze.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think that there were smart enough people in there to really know exactly what was going on, unless they had some kind of connections to the Germans who would tell him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, gosh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That would be-- it would be really a-- it would be hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had-- my mother had relatives that died in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, Warsaw, everybody was hoping that in Warsaw they are not going to kill the people like in Lodz, because Warsaw was not in the-- in the Third Reich, so it was the [NON-ENGLISH] they called it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said they're not going to kill people that are not in the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lodz was in the Third Reich, so they said, well, ultimately, they're gonna to kill everybody in there, whereas in Warsaw, they will not do that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Little did we-- anybody knew that what was going in Warsaw, that most people died there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was very few-- very few left over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once they started going in a-- in a bigger speed and more-- more active, you know, liquidation of the ghetto, they would go regularly, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would take 1,000 people, 1,200 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
